modName: Star Wars Galactic Credit Gold Coin Re-texture
summary: Gold coin re-textured to be a Galactic Credit
descriptionHtml:
\"Information is a commodity. It can be traded, sold, and purchased. And in the end, credits are only as useful as the secrets they can buy.\"
-Darth Bane

I re-textured the gold coins to look like  Star Wars Galactic Credits. I hope you like it and please endorse if you do. And there\'s still more Star Wars stuff to come ;-)
author: avenger86
